{"id":241139,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-四川自贡维权人士罗世模被关黑监狱两天/","date":"2012-07-20T08:46:22Z","modified":"2012-07-20T08:46:22Z","title":"维权网 | 四川自贡维权人士罗世模被关黑监狱两天遭暴力殴打（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-76wl7ea36Dc/UAj0sfMESYI/AAAAAAAAJeU/_qw_KVIVAYg/s1600/%E4%B8%962.JPG\"></a><br /><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'> </a><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-76wl7ea36Dc/UAj0sfMESYI/AAAAAAAAJeU/_qw_KVIVAYg/s320/%E4%B8%962.JPG\" width=\"262\" /></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>被殴打致伤的罗世模</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>﻿ </p>\n<div><span><br /></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员方芳报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日下午</span><span>，因“四川省实施‘两化’互动、统筹城乡发展战略工作会议”召开而被非法关押两天的维权人士罗世模先生遍体鳞伤的回到家中。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>因同一事件被软禁两天的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>自贡民间信访局</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>局长刘正有先生告诉本网信息员：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>号下午，罗世模先生被人从外面用车拉回来，放在小区楼下，送他的人就跑了，他被打的遍体鳞伤，左脚肿起很大无法走路，现正在医院治伤。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日，罗世模先生被从家中强行带走后关在黑监狱两天，期间，遭到看守他的东街办事处主任范文彬等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3-4</span><span>人的暴力殴打。罗世模多次拨打</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>报警警方无人出警！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>目前，正在医院接受治疗的罗世模先生不断敦促警方要求立案查处打人凶手，警方置之不理，打人凶手仍然逍遥法外！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>刘正有：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18990093533</span></div>\n<div><span>罗世模：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13183924409</span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-7717079101252957643?l=wqw2010.